<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"
      xmlns:tal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/tal"
      xmlns:metal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/metal"
      xmlns:i18n="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/i18n"
      i18n:domain="c3sPortal"
      metal:use-macro="base">
  <tal:block metal:fill-slot="content">     
    <!-- div id="middle" -->
    <div class="row">
      <div class="span16">
	<p class="app-welcome" i18n:translate="c3s-welcome-definition">
          Welcome to <strong i18n:name="C3S">C3S</strong>, a new Collecting Society being booted up.
        </p>
        <p i18n:translate="c3s-short-explanation">C3S is an abbreviation for 
	  <strong i18n:name="CreativeCommonsCollectingSociety">Creative Commons Collecting Society</strong></p>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="row">
      <div class="span6">      
      <h1 i18n:translate="headline_about">What is C3S?</h1>
	<p i18n:translate="">
	  C3S -- an abbreviation for Creative Commons Collecting Society -- is a new upcoming European collecting society
          for Artists and Bands to register their works: music released under Creative Commons and other free licenses.
	</p>
	<p i18n:translate="">
	  We expect the delivery of application to offlically become a registered 
	  and approved collecting society to happen at the end of 2012.
	</p>
	<p>
	  <strong><a href="/about" i18n:translate="read-more">Read more...</a></strong>
	</p>
      </div>

      <div class="span5  well">
        <h2 i18n:translate="">About C3S</h2>
          <ul class="foo">
            <li><a href="${request.route_url('about') + '#definition'}" 
		   i18n:translate="">What is C3S?</a></li>
            <li><a href="${request.route_url('about') + '#background'}" 
		   i18n:translate="">Who is doing C3S?</a></li>
            <li><a href="${request.route_url('about') + '#motivation'}" 
		   i18n:translate="">Why do we want to start C3S?</a></li>
            <li><a href="${request.route_url('about') + '#goals'}" 
		   i18n:translate="">What is C3S trying to become? What not?</a></li>
            <li><a href="${request.route_url('about') + '#roadmap'}" 
		   i18n:translate="">How is this project being realized?</a></li>
            <li><a href="irc://irc.freenode.net#OpenMusicContest.org" 
		   i18n:translate="">IRC Channel</a></li>
          </ul>
	</div>

    </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="span12">
	  <h2 i18n:translate="headline_goals">Goals</h2>
	  <ul>
	    <li i18n:translate="">equal rights (co-determination) for all members</li>
	    <li i18n:translate="">revenue generation for musicians using alternative licensing schemes</li>
	    <li i18n:translate="">free and legal usage of music in non-commercial contexts</li>
	    <li i18n:translate="">royalites based on works published (1:1)</li>
	    <li i18n:translate="">collect royalties only for works chosen by the artists</li>
	    <li i18n:translate="">reach 100% payout of royalties</li>
	    <li i18n:translate="">transparency</li>
	    <li i18n:translate="">promotion of culture</li>
	  </ul>
	</div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
	<div class="span4">
	  <h2 i18n:translate="">Register</h2>
	  <p><strong i18n:translate="">We need your support!</strong></p>
	  
	  <p i18n:translate="register-p1">
	    If you are ready and willing to register your musical works with C3S 
	    after it has been fully functional as a collecting society for
	    works under Creative Commons Licenses, 
	    and would like to become a member, please <a href="/support#register">
	      register here!</a>
	  </p>
	  
	  <p i18n:translate="register-p2">
	    The number of registered supporters is absolutely crucial for C3S 
	    to officially become approved as and allowed to be a collecting society.
	  </p>
	</div>
	
	<div class="span4">
	  <h2 i18n:translate="home-headline-artists">Artists</h2>
	  <dl>
	  <dd i18n:translate="register-p2">
	    The number of registered supporters is absolutely crucial for C3S 
	    to officially become approved as and allowed to be a collecting society.
	  </dd>
	  </dl>
	</div>
	<div class="span4">
	  <h2 i18n:translate="home-headline-partners">Sponsors and Partners</h2>

	  <p>
	    Duis tempor placerat turpis, nec viverra lorem hendrerit a. Nulla quis mollis eros. Aenean non magna venenatis metus imperdiet malesuada. Nam blandit, quam et euismod auctor, odio leo porttitor lorem, suscipit tristique massa sem sed neque. Vestibulum tempor interdum libero, at pulvinar purus suscipit eget. Cum sociis natoque penatibus et magnis dis parturient montes, nascetur ridiculus mus.
	  </p>

	</div>
      </div>

  </tal:block>
</html>
